Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.97,0:00:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有预约时间(硬比出V手势)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.87,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女英雄驾到
