Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.68,0:00:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘掉烦人的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ThankYou! 挖到宝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.82,0:00:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招财猫招啊招(客人来吧)
