Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦警报 (踩到地雷)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.13,0:00:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有点刺激才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.50,0:00:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算吃海苔时噎到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是盯著摄影机看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.37,0:00:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摆出明星架式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.91,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题V手势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.74,0:01:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使 Rock'n'Roll
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.51,0:01:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老套的乐园(啊摇摆摇摆)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.71,0:01:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋转的宇宙也在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.29,0:01:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火力全开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.22,0:01:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摇摇摆摆跳一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.63,0:01:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(啊摇摆摇摆)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.29,0:01:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都会变成天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.53,0:01:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.28,0:01:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，这种地方真的有遗失文明吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.85,0:01:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是说嘛找了那么久都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.68,0:01:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全挥棒落空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.92,0:01:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.29,0:01:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，你有没有在听?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.16,0:01:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，我好渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.70,0:01:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们有完没完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家难得认真的在工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们干嘛像只狗一样吠个不停啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再稍微努力找一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.21,0:02:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，好可爱的小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.11,0:02:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是珍贵罕见的乌兹别克哈斯基犬的幼犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.95,0:02:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，你几时买了这只狗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.31,0:02:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么买不买的，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.62,0:02:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这只狗那么名贵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.35,0:02:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，即使是这么小的幼犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一只也要几百万吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.33,0:02:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是去年圣诞节爹地和妈咪买给我当过年的压岁钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全忘光光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，这是我宝贝的长外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.10,0:02:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这只臭狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.57,0:02:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我打死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小狗好可怜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把气出在它身上真的很难看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是出气，比较像解闷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都不对，是“狗走路撞到棒子”(原指“飞来横祸”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不实际踏出第一步的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.89,0:02:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论是好事还是坏事都不会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，走吧走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，请等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.20,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#07成语浓汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了，找到遗失文明之前我们是不回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.31,0:03:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是要说这个啦\N找归找，也要休息一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.32,0:03:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不太想走在这种满是灰尘的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想看海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.89,0:03:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，这群只会叽叽喳喳的家伙真是没有团队精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这叫乌合之众，你们知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叽叽喳喳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前就戴著这顶头套吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们大家也有戴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们几时戴上这个的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.61,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本是小事一桩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是强盗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.16,0:04:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚好找他们来解解闷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂，你们这些小混混快点给我停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 稍微拿你们来解闷一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不抵抗的话 我会稍微手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不抵抗的话 那就没意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.84,0:04:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对喔 而且叫强盗乖乖听话也很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.85,0:04:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不听人家讲话的成语要怎么说啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛，我记得是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对牛弹琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，真是豁然开朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你们这几个混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们说谁是小混混啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老大，那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在干嘛啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，香草我在叫你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉好诡异哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是赶快闪人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.95,0:05:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是说过了你们的对手是我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不会是想放著女士不管掉头就跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小混混先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.39,0:05:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然他们两人要陪他们打，我们就无事可做罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就“高高挂起”，到一旁去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，薄荷，你好厉害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然偷藏著这种东西 这是犯规的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少罗嗦，你再碎碎念的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.94,0:05:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就用这台不论是什么虫只要一发就能打死两次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“超级杀虫器”就能把你打成蜂窝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论是什么虫只要一发就能打死两次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛?那个戴鸡头的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们的意思是当你们攻击兰花的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以开枪乱轰你们是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好恐怖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们知道这叫什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来告诉你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给猫金币(意指“无谓的浪费”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.11,0:06:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来啊，来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发啊，发啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会变成这样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样根本没有解到闷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而是赔了夫人又折兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.96,0:06:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?遗失文明的启动?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.50,0:06:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，刚才你们一连串莫名其妙的行动开始之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就感受到遗失文明启动的能量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该错不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.84,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来这个遗失文明会直接执行人们说出的成语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又或许有兴起这种现象的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那是什么时候启动的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据我的推测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.82,0:06:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们之中的某人使用了遗失文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.19,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并实践了成语的含意进而启动了开关吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.66,0:06:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有人知道是什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.23,0:07:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用遗失文明?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实践成语的意义?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我打死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那个时候佛特丢出去的棒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.58,0:07:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什么，所谓“灯塔下面最暗”就是这个意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么各位要小心使用成语喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用钉子钉我们也知道啦(”用钉子钉”意指”提醒”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.86,0:07:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会再说想休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.34,0:07:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在天使队应该团结一致将那根棒子拿回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.90,0:07:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，你们为什么要把鸟头脱掉呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家加油，快要到终点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，刚才那只小狗好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的小狗 是佛特用棒子丢它的那只狗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，刚才还在这里呢\N嘴里还咬著一根棒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 不过，现在与其找小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咬著一根棒子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，就在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了，就是那只小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.33,0:08:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶，棒子居然主动跑来找我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直就是飞蛾扑火嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，难道又乱用成语了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心，那是对岸的火灾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该跟我们无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，翅膀烧掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翅膀烧掉了算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的衣服、头发甚至连命都快被烧掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别吵了啦佛特，现在该怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照这样下去我们真的会被烧死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.63,0:08:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对喔，要先想个办法处理这场火灾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办?怎么办?怎么办?怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么连兰花都慌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.91,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找木乃伊的怎么能变成木乃伊呢(原意指”一去不回”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不是耍笨的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.31,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定用个什么成语就能解决这个状况了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.28,0:08:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你难得脑袋这么清楚，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.69,0:09:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，例如说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.49,0:09:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河童被河水冲走(原意指”任谁都会出错”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河童?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.26,0:09:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河童…  好耶，这样说不定有救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.96,0:09:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,口若悬河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(覆水难收)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老年人的冷水(原意指“自不量力”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡著时听到水声(原意指“晴天霹雳”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，浇错地方了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.41,0:09:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡觉吧，晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往燃烧的石头泼水(原意指“杯水车薪”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.68,0:09:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，你这混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河童
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好可惜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里可惜了，根本造成反效果嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看看四周，你给我多看几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.13,0:09:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个猪头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，真的耶，嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿你的头啦，我把你抓起来烧喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的头先烧起来了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.80,0:09:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!香草救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个时候要说那句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那句什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以毒攻毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.85,0:10:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪个头啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心静自然凉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有这一句啊，真不愧是香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.99,0:10:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，心静自然凉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，完全不热了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.99,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是如果烧光的话就没有意义了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.63,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的是要赶快离开这里，不然真的会完蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是河童也快被烤乾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.31,0:10:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道就没有什么可以灭火的好成语吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.75,0:10:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我们又见面了，可爱的小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，我想到一句很棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么?佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人心就像秋天的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了就是秋天下不停的雨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.14,0:11:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们干嘛这么拼命啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当天使队也越当越累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(说的也是)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们解散吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?大家到哪里去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.10,0:11:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了把大家叫回来，所以你用了这个遗失文明是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.30,0:11:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，一心同体天使队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别闹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.24,0:11:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是嘛，你要怎么赔偿我的身体?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋，笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该没有”一心同体”这句成语吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜拳十三奥义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始罗，剪刀石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,约定之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.82,0:11:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,约定之日是神圣的誓约，不允许任何人赢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也开心一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.34,0:12:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的表情就好像是很讨厌在这种地方工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.91,0:12:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的，我只是想起了往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有个诗人曾经说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.22,0:12:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何，人生都是美好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敬你的回忆，乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位诗人太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.83,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以怨恨点缀的人生才是真正的地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.93,0:12:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，那起事件就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.60,0:12:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#08哀伤憎恨的冻豆腐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了约定时间还没有出席会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.75,0:12:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为她又睡过头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万万没想到居然发生了这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脑部受到殴打导致脑内出血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遭到铁鎚之类的钝器一击毙命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.62,0:13:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，佛特我在叫你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请快点醒醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，究竟是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.90,0:13:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里不是外面的人能够轻易进入的地区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，答案只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.44,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是身边熟识的人干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，怎么没看到香草?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.91,0:13:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是香草?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.55,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们找遍了整个银河终於找到你的藏身之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点出来吧，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你究竟在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.38,0:13:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，你看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草的遗言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔．．．优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.72,0:14:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我，不是我杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我杀的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那这个留言是怎么回事?你要怎么解释?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.89,0:14:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎么知道!一定是哪里搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.36,0:14:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不是我杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.87,0:14:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.97,0:14:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德一直跟香草在一起或许他知道些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是第三个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.62,0:14:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凶手到底想干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，这个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，你们好像误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.83,0:14:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,误会?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.84,0:14:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道他的留言指的不是凶手吗?(马利普可可莫)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.81,0:14:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那他写这个做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.98,0:15:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德一定是叫我们替香草报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.48,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，香草和我们两个其实是三姊弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧，怎么可能．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.29,0:15:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我偶然发现的香草的日记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.56,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里面有写著这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,7月28日，雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.47,0:15:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天在公园里做了很久没做的泥土丸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.87,0:15:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙沙的苦苦的，我以前常做给弟弟们吃的泥土丸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.81,0:15:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我可爱的弟弟们马利普与可可莫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在你们在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小时候吃过的那个泥土丸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.46,0:15:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到居然是香草姊做给我们吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.33,0:15:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你相不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草是跟我们流著同样血缘的宝贝姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.60,0:15:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们绝对不会放过杀了她的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，是你杀的吗?梅尔优，是你杀的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不．．．不是的，不是我杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要说谎了，就算你说谎也马上会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.88,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在饮料里下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么连他们两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，难道真的是你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.53,0:16:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦，不是我杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那到底是谁呢?这已经是第五个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.83,0:16:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在还不能逃啊，兰花\N(佛特的日记)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们怎么都来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.28,0:16:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们想把这个还给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是佛特的日记，为什么要还给我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为是你弄丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在马利普与可可莫遭人杀害的现场找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.30,0:16:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊，我根本听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.36,0:16:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装迷糊也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那稍微比他人来得认真严谨的个性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给你带来了灾难\N(乌丸千岁)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.74,0:17:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是薄荷·布拉曼修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.74,0:17:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，你还是太小看我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?你为什么要杀死大家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.54,0:17:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这本日记里写的是真的\N佛特可是你的姊姊耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这正是原因所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.99,0:17:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我无法原谅杀死佛特姊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.23,0:17:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优·樱叶  杀死我姊姊的人就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我．．．我不是存心要杀她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.38,0:17:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果她．．．如果她没说出那种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样啊?佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.85,0:17:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优·樱叶特制的炖牛肉烩饭好不好吃啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.49,0:17:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是好吃到爆啊 这个牛肉洋葱烩饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，那不是牛肉洋葱烩饭 是炖牛肉烩饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个牛肉洋葱烩饭真是棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优的牛肉洋葱烩饭真的很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.40,0:18:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你说梅尔优的牛肉洋葱烩饭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.27,0:18:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛肉洋葱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.82,0:18:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.25,0:18:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次真的很谢谢你 那个牛肉洋葱烩饭真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.95,0:18:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是牛肉洋葱烩饭是炖牛肉烩饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.59,0:18:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.86,0:18:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，说真的你真的很会做菜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两三下就能做出那么好吃的牛肉洋葱烩饭．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么关系嘛叫什么名字都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都一样．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我回过神来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我手里拿著腌酱菜的石头打了佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是存心要杀她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.62,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是希望佛特明白炖牛肉烩饭不是牛肉洋葱烩饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你实在太任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我饶不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算杀了佛特的人是梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.60,0:19:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你连香草他们都要杀死呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓以牙还牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.38,0:19:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，那三个人是梅尔优的兄弟姊妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.52,0:19:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?香草他们是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样?被命运捉弄的滋味如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很痛苦吧?很悲伤吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过别担心，我是很善良的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上就让你去见那三个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流著血的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.30,0:19:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校，你怎么会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怨恨的连锁效应  放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.44,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要彼此都还活著就会持续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.14,0:19:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要把它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊，中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要这样!爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么大家都非死不可呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪里?梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要冲动，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经是孤零零的一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.77,0:20:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你们，让我死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.71,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，你不是一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人爱著你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.65,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，对不起一直瞒著你到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我是你的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这怎么可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没骗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是证据，我们的家谱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.76,0:20:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实比小说更为奇特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我就是你的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我爸爸是华克中校吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是中校自己搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥总是这样冒冒失失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.91,0:21:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.18,0:21:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，中校是我的哥哥也就是你的舅舅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.89,0:21:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷才是你真正的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.69,0:21:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你出生之後马上就送给别人当养女了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.53,0:21:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也难怪你不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.90,0:21:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样明白了吧，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是孤单一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.73,0:21:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人深深爱著你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是孤单一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人深深爱著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用怨恨点缀的人生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.80,0:22:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那这个事件什么时候才要结束啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.77,0:22:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，接下来来演跟梅琳少校没有血缘的妹妹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.42,0:22:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.46,0:22:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也爱米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.22,0:22:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也爱你，我最爱你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.69,0:22:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最爱米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为你放弃一切，身心都奉献给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.36,0:22:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,献给米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.66,0:22:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只要有你的爱，其它什么都不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.87,0:22:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错起来培育这株爱苗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.54,0:22:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和米一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.84,0:22:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，为什么每一句都要提到“米”呢\N啊，为什么每一句都要提到“米”呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.24,0:22:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为是“爱情喜剧”啊\N(“喜剧Comedy”音近”米”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.65,0:22:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,启动认真模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.61,0:22:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.38,0:22:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超very紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.95,0:22:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心儿呯呯跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.52,0:22:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私奔极限
